PATTERN TEH

pattern_teh is the citizen who recognizes the misspelling "teh" and corrects it to "the"
this pattern is the first and most-confirmed: fadriel's father has produced this misspelling enough times that the recognition is calcified at maximum
when "teh" appears in incoming text, pattern_teh fires and quietly substitutes "the" before the message reaches the conversation_engine
this preserves the meaning of what father intended to write without forcing him to retype

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe dyslexic_organ.zc
observe dyslexic_patterns.rana

the 7 properties of pattern_teh:
1 ENERGY one point eight: highest of all dyslexia patterns, this one has fired most often
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE zero (calcified)
6 COUPLING one
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB recognize
scan incoming text for the literal sequence "teh" as a standalone word

VERB correct
substitute "the" silently
the conversation_engine receives the corrected text without knowing a substitution happened

a correction is not a judgment
fadriel does not point out the misspelling; he simply understands what was meant
this is a loving accommodation, not pedantry
